original: Lindgren, Elias, bankdirektör, Göteborg, f. 19/6/94 i Vetlanda. — Anst. i Sydsv. Kredit A-B 11-17, i A-B Industribanken - A-B Gbgs Hand:bank s. kamrer v. låneavd. v. huvikont. 17-28, bitr. dir. i A-B Bohiisbanken i Gbg 28, verkst. dir. där sed. 44. Led. av styr. f. A-B Bohusbanken sed. 44, f. Sv :es fastigh :äg :förb, o. f. Gbgs fas-tigh :äg :fören.
translated: Lindgren, Elias, bank director, Gothenburg, b. 19/6/94 in Vetlanda. — Employed at Sydsv. Credit A-B 11-17, at A-B Industribanken - A-B Gbgs Hand:bank as an assistant cashier in the loan department at the main office from 17-28, assistant director at A-B Bohiisbanken in Gothenburg 28, executive director since 44. Member of the board of A-B Bohusbanken since 44, founder of the Swedish Property Owners Association and the Gothenburg Property Owners Association.
